Class MuteProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tigertext.ttandroid.mute.MuteProcessor

  • public class MuteProcessor
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is in charge of handling any events that server may send us regarding mute events. All public methods are meant for use by client
